\description{
Provides a pipe-friendly framework to performs one and two sample
 Wilcoxon tests.

 See the Datanovia tutorial
 \href{https://www.datanovia.com/learn/biostatistics/two-groups/wilcoxon-test-in-r}{Wilcoxon Test in R}
